        {
            "title": "恒瑞醫藥首季盈利升逾1% 今早初段股價逆市造好",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒瑞醫藥(01276)昨天收市後派首季成績表，盈利增長逾20%；該股今早逆市造好，最多超超過6%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">該股今早一度衝上71.3元，升6.66%；截至上午約10時16分報69.9元，升幅收窄至4.56%，暫時成交已達2.61億元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15909417-%e6%81%92%e7%91%9e%e9%86%ab%e8%97%a5%e9%a6%96%e5%ad%a3%e7%9b%88%e5%88%a9%e5%8d%87%e9%80%be1-%e4%bb%8a%e6%97%a9%e5%88%9d%e6%ae%b5%e8%82%a1%e5%83%b9%e9%80%86%e5%b8%82%e9%80%a0%e5%a5%bd",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250515_FI_source-web_01726-IPO.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-23 10:17:59",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "港股失守兩萬六 智譜逆市創新高",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">外圍股市造好未能帶挈港股，大市今早低開後跌勢迅速擴大，開市不久即失守兩萬六關口。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">截至上午約10時08分，恒生指數報25986點，跌176點或0.68%；早前最低曾見25872點，跌290點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">科股領跌，恒生科技指數暫報4897點，跌1.34%。騰訊(00700)跌逾1%，阿里巴巴(09988)暫仍力保不失，微升不足0.1%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">個別熱門科技半新股續炒上，智譜(02513)逆市創新高，暫報1070點，升5.82%；群核科技(00068)也升逾1%，MiniMax(00100)則反覆跌約0.6%</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15909371-%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e5%a4%b1%e5%ae%88%e5%85%a9%e8%90%ac%e5%85%ad-%e6%99%ba%e8%ad%9c%e9%80%86%e5%b8%82%e5%89%b5%e6%96%b0%e9%ab%98",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/HKSTOCK-6.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-23 10:15:09",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "人行今進行5億人幣逆回購操作",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">人民銀行今日進行5億元(人民幣‧下同)的7天逆回購操作，操作利率為1.40%，與先前持平；今日5億元逆回購到期。</p>\n</div>",
