            "title": "滬指開市升4點 深成指升56點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">內地股市初段偏好，上證綜指以4110點開市，升4點或0.11%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">深證成指開市報15234點，亦升56點或0.38%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滬深300指數升16點或0.34%，開報4816點；創業板指數開市報3769點，升16點或0.43%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15909227-%e6%bb%ac%e6%8c%87%e9%96%8b%e5%b8%82%e5%8d%874%e9%bb%9e-%e6%b7%b1%e6%88%90%e6%8c%87%e5%8d%8756%e9%bb%9e",
