            "title": "即月期指開報26207點 高水44點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">即月期指開報26207點，升46點，較上日現貨收市報26163點高水44點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">即月科指期貨開報4988點，升26點，高水24點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">即月國指期貨開報8830點，升31點，高水28點。</p>\n</div>",
